---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Now | Gde Juliartha";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h1>Now</h1>
  <p>My current focus, learning, interest, and hobbies.</p>
  <h2>July 1, 2026</h2>
  <div class="last-update">
    <div class="update">
      <p>💼 Professional</p>
      <p>
        Working on two web development projects while also learning HTML, CSS,
        and JavaScript more deeply this time. I'm back to explore product/UX
        design and web development roles this time. Honestly, feeling more
        excited coding in VS Code rather than designing in Figma right now.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="update">
      <p>🔍 Learning</p>
      <p>
        Currently excited with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React. Also learning
        about JAMStack and static-site generator. Been pretty obsessed with
        these technologies since the start of the year. In the midst of AI hype,
        I want to understand the fundamentals first and honing my craft. I'm
        still use AI for exploration though and debugging (handling those
        dependencies in the deployment sure helps a lot).
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="update">
      <p>📚 Reading</p>
      <p>
        I always read more than one book at a time. Currently reading 'Before
        the Coffe Gets Cold' by Toshikazu Kawaguchi, '12 Rules for Life' by
        Jordan Peterson, and 'How to Stop Worrying and Start Living' by Dale
        Carnegie.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="update">
      <p>🎧 Listening</p>
      <p>
        I'm pretty much into Fred Again for the latest three years. His latest
        collaboration with Thomas Bangalter has been in my playlist rotation for
        quite a while.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="update">
      <p>🎾 Hobbies</p>
      <p>
        Tennis has been part of my life since 2023. Enjoy both playing it and
        watching the professional competition since. Currently I don't play much
        due to work and hoping to get back on the court more frequently soon.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .last-update {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .update {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      > p {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
